Project Name

AI-Powered Interview Preparation and Assessment Platform

Problem Statement

Job seekers and working professionals often struggle to prepare effectively for technical interviews due to the lack of realistic interview practice environments, organized question repositories, and personalized performance feedback. Existing interview preparation platforms primarily focus on static question banks and multiple-choice assessments, which do not adequately simulate real interview scenarios where candidates are expected to verbally explain concepts and demonstrate their knowledge.

There is a need for a centralized web-based interview preparation platform that allows administrators to manage department-specific interview content and enables candidates to practice interviews through interactive assessments. The system shall allow administrators to create departments and subdomains such as Mobile Development, Web Development, Backend Development, Database Technologies, and other technical areas. Administrators should be able to upload question-and-answer repositories in bulk through supported file formats such as PDF, DOCX, or TXT, and the system shall automatically extract, categorize, and store the content within the appropriate departments.

Candidates shall be able to select a department, experience level, and desired number of interview questions before initiating a mock interview session. During the interview, questions shall be presented in a randomized manner. Candidates should be able to provide responses either by typing or through voice input. Voice responses shall be converted to text and evaluated against the expected answers stored in the system.

The platform shall analyze candidate responses using predefined evaluation criteria, generate performance scores, identify strengths and weaknesses, and provide detailed feedback reports. The system shall maintain interview history, track progress over time, and help candidates identify knowledge gaps and areas requiring improvement. The overall objective is to provide a realistic, scalable, and data-driven interview preparation experience that improves candidate confidence and interview readiness.